{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8a26d96c79","title":"中央转发贵州省委三级干部会议情况汇报的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5c903cff1c","index":0,"year":1959,"month":9,"day":4,"articleId":"8a26d96c79"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"b8dd2153b3","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8a26d96c79","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共贵州省委1959年9月2日的这一电话汇报的主要内容是：一贵州省委三级干部会议讨论形势、揭露矛盾的第一阶段已经结束。总的看来，绝大部分同志是拥护党的总路线的，有糊涂看法的同志，多数都主动作了检讨，得到了教育。二、有右倾思想和在大风浪中曾暂时动摇的同志，多数是对中央第二次郑州会议以来的一系列政策措施从消极方面去理解，因而对去年的大跃进和人民公社制度发生了怀疑。三、从9月3日起，将重新划分小组，分别对问题严重的人进行批判。"},{"id":"83b226f269","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8a26d96c79","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。"},{"id":"aeb7c96d4c","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8a26d96c79","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、中央办公厅主任。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3fa7581baa","type":"title","text":"中央转发贵州省委三级干部会议情况汇报的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8a26d96c79"},{"id":"b8dd2153b3","type":"paragraph","text":"此件很有参考价值，发各省、市、区党委","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8a26d96c79"},{"id":"83b226f269","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8a26d96c79"},{"id":"aeb7c96d4c","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五九年九月四日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8a26d96c79"},{"id":"aa81db271f","type":"paragraph","text":"E刘问、彭真同志阅后，尚昆即办","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8a26d96c79"}],"page":{"id":"5fc977e25c","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8a26